# Scene Assembler vs XR Voice — locked URL map

See workspace rule `spark-msf-xr-url-separation.mdc` and `docs/NVIDIA_XR_AI_INTEGRATION.md`.

| Product | Surface proxy | Env vars |
|---------|---------------|----------|
| Scene Assembler | **:8453** (`npm run msf-proxy`) | `VITE_MSF_PUBLIC_URL` |
| XR Voice | **:8443** (`npm run xr-hub-proxy`) | `VITE_XR_HUB_URL` |

Run both proxies: `npm run dev:spark-proxies`. Verify: `npm run verify:dev-proxies`.

Never assign XR Voice to `:8453` or Scene Assembler to `:8443` on Surface.
